These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: lacrosse, rugby, golf, soccer, cricket, snowboarding
The people use 6 different means of transport: scooter, ship, skateboard, snowmobile, taxi, tram
1. the person driving the scooter is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person driving the scooter is between the person driving the tram and the person driving the taxi##2
5. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
8. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person driving the skateboard##1
9. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |     3      |  4   |     5      |    6    |
| Sport         | cricket     | golf | lacrosse | soccer | snowboarding      | rugby |
| Transport   | snowmobile | taxi  | scooter    | tram | skateboard | ship    |

