.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: comedy, horror, mystery, satire, scientific, time-travel
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: daisy, balloon-flower, dahlia, poppy, orchid, bellflower
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 2. the person who growspoppy is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
 4. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 5. the person watching mystery movies is the person who growspoppy##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 7. the person who growsdahlia is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who growsorchid is in an even position##4
 9. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
10. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |      5      |    6    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | satire  | scientific | horror   | time-travel | mystery |
| Flower   | dahlia | orchid | balloon-flower    | bellflower | daisy   | poppy   |

