.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: ambient, metal, r&b, rock, salsa, soul
City: prague, new-york, edinburgh, liverpool, colone, rome
1. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
4. the fan of rock is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
6. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
7. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the fan of metal##1
8. the person traveling to prague is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person traveling to liverpool is the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |    3    |       4       |     5      |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | ambient    | salsa | r&b     | metal         | rock       | soul     |
| City         | prague | edinburgh  | new-york | rome | colone | liverpool |

