.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-4::.
House: modern, gothic-revival, ranch-style, cape-cod, victorian, palace
The people use 6 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, skateboard, train, tram, van
1. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
2. the victorian house is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
3. the modern house is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the train is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the skateboard is the ranch-style house##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
7. the victorian house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
8. the modern house is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
9. the person driving the van is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| House   | modern | gothic-revival     | ranch-style     | cape-cod | victorian | palace |
| Transport     | van    | motorbike | skateboard | train  | tram       | boat      |

