.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: documentary, musical, romance, scientific, time-travel, western
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: punk, house, blues, electronic, hip-hop, pop
 1. the fan of electronic is between the person watching romance movies and the fan of blues##2
 2. the person watching musical movies is the fan of pop##1
 3. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 4. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 5. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 6. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
 8. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 9. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
10. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
11. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
12. the fan of electronic is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |     4      |     5      |    6    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | scientific | documentary | western    | romance    | musical |
| Music-Genre     | house         | punk       | blues  | electronic | hip-hop | pop   |

