 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the writer##1
 6. the software-developer is on the right of the engineer##1
 7. the engineer is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
 8. the nurse is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 9. the analyst is in an even position##4
10. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2       |         3          |    4     |     5     |   6    |
