.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-10::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, hot-chocolate, lemonade, milk, water
There are 6 different nationalities: pakistani, french, colombian, turkish, polish, egyptian
 1. the turkish is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking milk##2
 2. the polish is on the far left##1
 3. the egyptian is on the left of the french##1
 4. the person drinking water is the turkish##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 6. the colombian is on the far right##1
 7. the colombian is the person drinking cola##1
 8. the pakistani is on the left or right of the colombian##3
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is the polish##1
10. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |       3       |   4   |     5     |    6    |
| Beverage    | almond-milk | lemonade | hot-chocolate | water | milk      | cola    |
| Nationality   | polish       | egyptian      | french     | turkish  | pakistani | colombian |

