 5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 8. the person drinking sprite is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
11. the person who's birthday is in june is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |    4    |    5     |  6   |
