.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-20::.
There 6 different types of food: banana, blueberry, garlic, mango, onion, pear
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: fantasy, romance, sports, adventure, crime, superhero
 1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
 2. the person eating onion is in an even position##4
 3. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 4. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
 5. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 6. the person eating banana is the person watching crime movies##1
 7. the person eating garlic is in an even position##4
 8. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person eating onion and the person watching romance movies##2
10. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating pear##1
11. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
12. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |      2      |   3    |   4    |       5        |     6      |
| Food   | banana    | garlic      | mango  | onion  | pear           | blueberry  |
| Movie-Genre    | crime | romance | fantasy | adventure | superhero | sports |

 